    • 构造器详细资料

      • RMatGraph

        public RMatGraph(org.apache.flink.api.java.ExecutionEnvironment env,
                 RandomGenerableFactory<T> randomGeneratorFactory,
                 long vertexCount,
                 long edgeCount)
        Generate a directed or undirected power-law Graph using the Recursive Matrix (R-Mat) model.
        参数:
        env - the Flink execution environment
        randomGeneratorFactory - source of randomness
        vertexCount - number of vertices
        edgeCount - number of edges

    • 方法详细资料

      • setConstants

        public RMatGraph<T> setConstants(float A,
                                 float B,
                                 float C)
        The parameters for recursively subdividing the adjacency matrix. Setting A = B = C = 0.25 emulates the Erdős–Rényi model. Graph500 uses A = 0.57, B = C = 0.19.
        参数:
        A - likelihood of source bit = 0, target bit = 0
        B - likelihood of source bit = 0, target bit = 1
        C - likelihood of source bit = 1, target bit = 0
        返回:
        this

      • setNoise

        public RMatGraph<T> setNoise(boolean noiseEnabled,
                             float noise)
        Enable and configure noise. Each edge is generated independently, but when noise is enabled the parameters A, B, and C are randomly increased or decreased, then normalized, by a fraction of the noise factor during the computation of each bit.
        参数:
        noiseEnabled - whether to enable noise perturbation
        noise - strength of noise perturbation
        返回:
        this

        从接口复制的说明: GraphGenerator

        返回:
